PyTorch conda environment for use with DeltaAI (CUDA 12.9)

Includes: jupyter, jupyterlab, matplotlib, pandas, scipy,
          scikit-learn, nvitop, mpi4py, tensorboard, wandb

Quick start (on compute node):
  module load python/miniforge3_pytorch/2.10.0
  conda activate base
  python -c "import torch; print(torch.cuda.is_available())"

For Jupyter notebook support (Open OnDemand):
  setup-kernel

